      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing zero signs of wear on the upholstery or controls. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine is powerful and quiet, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and every electronic feature works exactly as intended. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle that has been meticulously garaged and maintained to the highest possible standards.",
